Pinsir (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0126: Magmar
Pokémon
#0128: Tauros →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Pinsir (TCG Pocket).

Pinsir has been featured on 22 different cards since it debuted in the Jungle expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Pinsir cards are normally Grass-type Basic Pokémon.
